item.content:encoded: Our Side Chair is an epitome of a piece-of-art. Its play on clean lines and designs makes this chair very appealing to a home decor that appreciates standout pieces. Don’t overlook the details of the side chair which is made of durable wood frame and covered in fabric upholstery that makes it extremely inviting to your guests. Its sleek legs are built to create balance and the back seat includes exposed zip zag lines that makes this chair aesthetically pleasing and agreeable to any form. Quality Smooth, ergonomic body and upholstered seat provide extra comfort and lumbar support, comfortable upholstered seat made of durable fabric, suitable structure, built-in enough stability, screw fixing, strong and durable.
